The paper focuses on network traffic forensic analysis, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The study also involves capturing and analyzing network packets, which relates to network infrastructure (cs.DC) and network protocols (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of a simulator, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the study involves investigating cybercrime, which falls under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
